    <p>
      From apartments and rooms to treehouses and boats: stay in unique spaces in 192 countries.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="home-page group">

    <a href="<%= room_url(@feature_two) %>">
      <img src="<%= @feature_two.pictures.first.image(:profile) %>">
      <div class="featured-room-title" id="feature-title-two">
        <%= @feature_two.display_title %>
      </div>
    </a>


    <h3 class="text-special">Host</h3>
    <p>
      Renting out your unused space could pay your bills or fund your next vacation.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="home-page group">

    <a href="<%= room_url(@feature_three) %>">
